data.title: IPM Citrus Pests
data.meta_description: IPM Citrus Pests - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides information on various citrus pests including whiteflies, ants, aphids, southern green stink bugs, mealybugs, scale, citrus leaf miner, citrus butterfly, leaf-footed plant bug, and their impacts and controls. It also discusses integrated pest management strategies for whiteflies, ants, and aphids in citrus crops, including monitoring, mechanical and biological controls, and cultural practices.
